Package net.deltapvp.library.common.logging

Interface PluginLogger

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    JavaPluginLogger, Log4jPluginLogger, Slf4jPluginLogger
    public interface PluginLogger
    Represents the logger instance being used by Library on the platform.

    Messages sent using the logger are sent prefixed with the Library tag, and on some implementations will be colored depending on the message type.
